                   Department of Alcohol and Drug Programs



                                  About Us


   ADP's Vision Statement

   Californians are healthy contributing persons in communities free of
   alcohol and other drug related problems.

   ADP's Mission Statement

   The Department provides leadership, policy and coordination and
   investments, in the planning, development, and implementation and
   evaluation of a comprehensive statewide alcohol and other drug abuse
   prevention, treatment and recovery services delivery system.

